original_title: CycleOps realRides Race Day Trainer DVD
overview: Make the most of your alone-time with the CycleOps Real Rides RaceDay Indoor Trainer DVD. Quench your thirst for race-day action as you ride along with pro-coach Robbie Ventura in an elite-level criterium race. Bicycle-mounted cameras put you right in the race with Robbie as he kills it.
title: CycleOps realRides Race Day Trainer DVD
